title: SD Revisited: Side Effects of Being in Your 30s
description:
This week, we revisit our homage to the decade of your 30s! If you’re wondering if you’re where you should be, how you’ll get where you going, or simply if 30 really is the new 20, we speak on it and hopefully help you get closer to figuring it out!
